.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.52</biblScope></bibl>, etc.: it was concave, and hence sts. used as a vessel to hold liquid, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg004.perseus-grc1:540\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">540</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n93101.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> metaph., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">shield, defence</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">βωμός, ἄρρηκτον ς</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg001.perseus-grc1:190\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Supp.\">Supp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">190</biblScope></bibl>. (Prob. cogn. with Skt. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tvác-</tr_> 'skin, hide'.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}